Chike-Ezekpeazu Osebuka (amụrụ ya n'ọnwa Jenụwarị 28, 1993), nke ama ama n'aha ogbo ya CHIKE, bụ onye Naijiria na-agụ
gwue
abụ, onye negwude abụ na onye na-eme ihe nkiri
A maara ya maka isonye na asọmpi eziokwu Nigeria Project Fame West Africa wee mechaa n'ọkwa nke abụọ na Oge 1 nke Voice Nigeria
Chike mere mpụta mbụ ya dị ka Mayowa Badmus na ihe ngosi Africa Magic Show telenovela Battleground
Chike bu onye Onitsha, nke dị na Steeti Anambra na Naijiria
O si n’ezinụlọ nwere ụmụ anọ
Ezinụlọ ya nwere nkà n'ịgụ egwu, nke metụtara mkpebi ya ịchụso ọrụ egwu
Ọ bụ onye gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Covenant nwere nzere na Injinia Kọmputa
E gosipụtara Chike dị ka onye asọmpi na Project Fame West Africa
E wepụrụ ya mgbe o ruru Top 10
Chike ji ihe mkpuchi nke James Arthur 'Roses' gbara akwụkwọ maka Voice Nigeria
Ndị nkuzi anọ ahụ tụgharịrị ya oche ha wee họrọ isonye na otu Patoranking
N'ọgbọ agha ahụ, ọ rụrụ Mario 's " Ka m hụ gị n'anya " ya na onye asọmpi Team Patoranking ọzọ wee họrọ ya ka ọ gaa n'ọzọ na-esote
N'ime izu mbụ nke ihe ngosi ndụ, ọ rụrụ "Ọ bụghị Nwanyị ahụ" site n'aka onye nkuzi Dare Art Alade wee nweta nzọpụta n'aka onye nkuzi ya
N'ime izu nke abụọ nke ihe ngosi ndụ, ọ rụrụ The Weeknd 's " Earned It " wee zọpụta ya site na ntuli aka ọha
Ọ rụkwara nsụgharị nke " M Gonna Be (500 Miles) " nke ndị Proclaimers wee nweta nzọpụta ikpeazụ nke onye nchịkwa ya nke oge
Maka agba nke ọkara ikpeazụ, ọ rụrụ "Pullover" nke Kcee na Wizkid
Na ngwụcha, Chike mere mkpuchi nke Bob Marley na ndị Wailers 's " No Woman No Cry " na Kiss Daniel 's "Mama"
Ọ gụchara dị ka onye na-agba ọsọ nke oge, A'rese sitere na Team Waje na-abịa na mbụ
Ka Voice Nigeria gachara, Chike bịanyere aka na Universal Republic yana ndị asọmpi anọ kachasị elu na ihe nkiri ahụ
Ọ wepụtara otu Fancy U nke mpụta mbụ ya na Disemba 2016 n'okpuru Universal Republic, na-ewepụta vidiyo egwu ya na mbido 2017
Emekwara Chike ka ọ bụrụ onye nnọchi anya Airtel Nigeria yana ndị asaa ndị ọzọ meriri Voice Nigeria
N'April 2017, akwadoro na Chike bụ onye Africa Magic mere ka ọ rụọ ọrụ Mayowa Badmus na ihe nkiri telivishọn aha ya bụ Battleground
Chike hapụrụ Universal Republic na Nọvemba 2017 ka ọ bụrụ onye nka nwere onwe ya
Ọ wepụtara otu ya ọzọ, akpọrọ "Ndị mara mma," na February 2018
Chike weputara ọba egwu 14 ya akpọrọ Boo of the Booless' nwere arụmọrụ pụrụ iche na ihe nkiri 2020 Big Brother Lockdown ihe nkiri.
